title: HOUR 3- Adam Beasley Oct 21, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Adam Beasley Oct 21, 2020
description:
Adam Beasley tells Dan that had their been an off season in the NFL that Tua would have perhaps been the day 1 starter for the Dolphins. Adam says that it was just time to start working Tua into the lineup for the future of the team.
